### Item 2: Sensitive File Scanning Campaign
- **item_id:** BC-WEB-SCAN-001
- **campaign_shape:** spray
- **suspected_compromised_src_ips:** 185.177.72.22, 185.177.72.49, 185.177.72.51, 185.177.72.52
